put.mlc.utils

Class MultiThreadEvaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • mulan.evaluation.Evaluator
      • put.mlc.utils.MultiThreadEvaluator

  • public class MultiThreadEvaluator
extends mulan.evaluation.Evaluator
    Evaluator class based on mulan.evaluation.Evaluator. It divides the prediction process into threads (by instances). This is experimental beta version.
    Author:
    Arkadiusz Jachnik
